Welcome to DarkOS.

Commands:
  help                   show DarkOS help topics
  help network           show networking commands
  network-status         check IP, routes, DNS, and ping
  chromium                  default web browser
  network-up             retry network driver loading and DHCP
  dpk update             update Alpine-backed package indexes
  dpk add xterm          install packages
  reboot                 reboot DarkOS
  poweroff               power off DarkOS
  KDE Plasma 6.7         starts automatically on Wayland
  posix-check            check musl/POSIX runtime pieces
  weston                 start a Wayland compositor
  darkelf /bin/ls        inspect an ELF executable
